<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=672&amp;p=700#p700"><![CDATA[
11/13(Sun.) Itaewon crush: South Korea demands justice for young as thousands protest/ Europe faces tough decisions over nuclear power(Host: Danny)<br /><br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a Zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------<br />Session I: Itaewon crush: South Korea demands justice for young as thousands protest<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-63526479">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-63526479</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Did you ever hear about that tragedy? What kinks of information did you get at the first time? Was that factual and accurate? Where did you get the information?<br />2.Would you prefer crowded places? What is the most important thing when you are in a crowded place. <br />3.What is the common reason for accidents? How to prevent?<br />Could you share any story to us? (any accident or way to prevent)<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------<br />Session II: Europe faces tough decisions over nuclear power<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-63245112">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-63245112</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.What do you think of the news?<br />2.We know that, a critical global issue. But what is the main problem you think? Politics? Science? Consumerism? Or any else?<br />3.The previous question is about the duty of governments, companies, or any group. How about every individual? What can we do to survive from this period?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Fri Nov 11, 2022 9:59 am</p><hr />
